вЂў /packs: Manage packs (install, enable, disable, uninstall)
вЂў /reload-mcp: Reload MCP config and refresh MCP tools for this session
вЂў /resume: Show the latest interrupted-turn resume note
вЂў /approvals: Show current one-time, session, and persistent approvals
вЂў /revoke: Revoke a persistent approval by id
вЂў /yolo: Toggle session YOLO/open mode; hard safety blocks still apply
вЂў /cron: Manage scheduled tasks
вЂў /trust: Trust this workspace for proactive local work
вЂў /untrust: Revoke workspace trust
вЂў /workspace.trust.status: Show whether the current workspace is trusted
вЂў /doctor: Run a quick in-session health check
вЂў /workflow: Workflow operator commands (status, pause, resume, steer, trace, etc.)
